# Grid System & Layout Constraints

## Breakpoints
- **Mobile**: < 1024px (`lg:` is the main breakpoint)
- **Desktop**: ≥ 1024px

## Site Widths
- Full site width: `max-w-site` = 1440px (header, footer span full viewport)
- Content container: `max-w-content` = 1200px → always `max-w-content mx-auto`
- Defined in `apps/web/src/style.css` `@theme` block (NOT in tailwind.config.js)

## `.grid-12` Utility (defined in style.css)
- **Mobile**: 4 columns, 20px gap → container uses `px-5`
- **Desktop**: 12 columns, 24px gap → container uses `px-3`

```tsx
// ✅ Page article wrapper
<article className="max-w-content mx-auto px-5 lg:px-3 pt-24 pb-16">
  <div className="grid-12">
    <div className="col-span-4 lg:col-span-6">...</div>   {/* half on desktop, full on mobile */}
    <div className="col-span-4 lg:col-span-6">...</div>
  </div>
</article>
```

## Column Span Reference (col-span-N)
| Mobile (4-col) | Desktop (12-col) | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `col-span-4` | `col-span-4` | Full-width mobile, 1/3 desktop |
| `col-span-2` | `col-span-4` | Half mobile, 1/3 desktop |
| `col-span-4 lg:col-span-6` | | Half desktop, full mobile |
| `col-span-4 lg:col-span-3` | | Quarter desktop, full mobile |

## Margins
- Article horizontal padding: `px-5` mobile (20px), `lg:px-3` desktop (12px)
- CTA box mobile margin: `mx-4 my-4` mobile, `lg:mx-0 lg:my-0` desktop

## Explicit Grid Override
For sections that need a fixed column count regardless of `grid-12` context:
```tsx
<ul className="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5">  {/* always 4 on desktop */}
```
